@misc @refillreminder
Feature: Customer is able Opens his personal email and performs required operations

#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@RXBATCH-RR-1
Scenario: Customer Executes the Refill Reminder's File Processing Job

Given  "RXBATCH-RR-1" Customer starts the scenario:
| InputFileName | SheetName | RowId        |
| QC-RXBATCH    | RR        | RXBATCH-RR-1 |

Then "RXBATCH-RR-1" Customer ftp the file for the batch job:
| InputFileName | SheetName  | RowId  |
| BatchData     | RR    	 | rrFTP1 |

Then "RXBATCH-RR-1" Customer run the commands for the batch job:
| InputFileName | SheetName  | RowId   			 |
| BatchData     | RR	     | rrFileProcessing1 |

Then "RXBATCH-RR-1" Customer run the commands for the batch job:
| InputFileName | SheetName  | RowId   			  |
| BatchData     | RR	     | rrEmailProcessing1 |


Then "RXBATCH-RR-1" Customer finished testing the scenario:
| InputFileName | SheetName | RowId        |
| QC-RXBATCH    | RR        | RXBATCH-RR-1 |


