@RXBATCH-RR-2
Scenario: Customer Verifies the Email Generated by Refill Reminders Email Processing Job

Given  "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer starts the scenario:
| InputFileName | SheetName | RowId        |
| QC-RXBATCH    | RR        | RXBATCH-RR-2 |

Given "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer login to the walgreens.com:
| InputFileName | SheetName  | RowId          		 |
| CommonData    | login      | RefillReminderuser1	 |

Given "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer login to the Email Client:
| InputFileName  | SheetName | RowId          	  |
| CommonData     | login     | RefillReminderuser1|

And "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer goes to the Inbox for the email client:
| InputFileName  | SheetName | RowId          |
| CommonData     | login     | nonloyaltyuser1|

Then "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer opens the required Email:
|	EmailType     	   |
|ReplytoRefillReminder |

And "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer validates the information on the Refill Reminders Email:
| ReplyToEmail   | ChangeYourPrivacyPreferenceLink  |  
| yes	         | Yes 	                            |  

And "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer goes to the Inbox for the email client:
| InputFileName  | SheetName | RowId           |
| CommonData     | login     | nonloyaltyuser6 |

And "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer Archive the required Email:
| InputFileName  | SheetName 	| EmailSubject      | ArchiveFolderName  |
| CommonData     | GenaralInfo  | EmailSubjectLine4 | ArchiveFolderName1 |

Then "RXBATCH-RR-2" Customer finished testing the scenario:
| InputFileName | SheetName | RowId        |
| QC-RXBATCH    | RR        | RXBATCH-RR-2 |

